itemDescription: member of the third cohort of female students to study at the University of St Andrews

wikipedia_page.main: Janet (Jessy) Thomson Philip (OBE) was a member of the third cohort of female students to study at the University of St Andrews and was School Secretary at the London School for Economics (LSE) from 1920 to 1939.

response: *November 26 - Janet (Jessy) Thomson Philip, School Secretary at the London School for Economics (d.  1959)
